    <abstract id="aspace_713d5f0152bda22291b7540a33db8ab3">The Robert Morris College Faculty Federation, Local No. 3412 of the American Federation of Teachers was certified by the National Labor Relations Board on October 8, 1974 as the collective bargaining agent for full-time faculty of the college.  This collection documents the disbandment of the Faculty Senate at Robert Morris College and the organization of Local 3412.</abstract>
